{"tid":380842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★追游b錢  葛珮帆：追到天腳底都要追！","createTime":"2017-08-30T12:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T15:14:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a15993e3804b5f4646fded9eca67581b45d518d","tid":380842,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"葛珮帆昨晚於facebook分享相關報道，留言「追！追到天腳底都要追！」她又說，兩人一開始便拿取全數預支金額，「從來冇做過嘢，又搬走晒立法會辦事處嘅嘢，而家一毫子都唔還，係咪明搶納稅人錢」。<br />\n葛珮帆亦質疑若兩人申請破產，是否便毋須還款。<br />\n葛珮帆上周五已曾評論宣誓覆核案，並要求兩人「回水」，「呢個世界有無咁無賴嘅人架？愈睇（相關新聞）愈嬲，愈睇愈㷫」。<br />\n游蕙禎昨日向《明報》表示，不會還錢；梁頌恆則說可以退回已購買的物資，但「看不到有相關法律理據退回款項」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170830/s00001/1504077136265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170830%2Fs00001%2F1504077136265&d=8vt1WIO3n2tQAERcszDr4I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9ad08ad3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170830%2Fs00001%2F1504077136265&h=8598c0db\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170830/s00001/1504077136265</a>"},{"pid":"85e5759b21d57e1fd9d6eae2bdee19ef0a8d3c6d","tid":380842,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170830/s00001/f47d30fa0c25a726bdb5b608323b2241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170830%2Fs00001%2Ff47d30fa0c25a726bdb5b608323b2241.jpg&h=2f2c4d83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a6e7a341f64baaa6f8c5985519ffc647cd9428c","tid":380842,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"睇左 游b腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caded1b198c47798971a324e1351e01666297eb4","tid":380842,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0